{"tid":767614,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"送俾連登巴絲既破處歌 - 歡樂春宵","createTime":"2018-08-04T16:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T16:54:23.000Z","uid":181793,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f5df784e98017cb7c9b44c1152dc0414d4356e","tid":767614,"uid":181793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"從夢裡伊甸   來到我枕邊<br />\n洞與棍之間   就只差一吋<br />\n這夜擒住妳   真實地癡纏<br />\n怕沒床技   妳又嫌短<br />\n<br />\n來替妳寬衣   除剩了黑絲<br />\n為破處一刻   大家都不客氣<br />\n相貌唔艷美   一樣易扯旗<br />\n不敢好奇   熄燈上妳<br />\n<br />\n房事   傳聞很痛<br />\n秘密現在被揭曉<br />\n明日想起   我們同樣回味心跳<br />\n歡樂春宵   嬌吟嗲叫<br />\n女上男下繼續纏繞<br />\n<br />\n談情一世   最大願望被吔蕉<br />\n含入一點   再來男上   床亦濕了<br />\n歡樂春宵   忍著尖叫<br />\n搏命亂搖   不能罷了<br />\n<br />\n歡樂春宵   呻吟歡笑<br />\n告別寂寥   青頭護照"},{"pid":"64e2f3ec48c8e923eaa199682045faf1df10872b","tid":767614,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e3f8c8771ca6979f37a5d8ed8f6d3c8a31d71c","tid":767614,"uid":98151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"作得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7ab48c13bf466bc8a2fa32b9af935d04b128b4","tid":767614,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e5322a103601242c566f5a4ea6d57b76c11c76","tid":767614,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"好撚正"},{"pid":"ed833d28cc86f5566c15bf8a491aa2c691c3256d","tid":767614,"uid":183385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T20:38:47.000Z","ms